                                                                                        <a href="https://github.com/knpuniversity/symfony2-rest/edit/master/knpu/episode5/restrict-valid-programmer-input.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-circle pull-right js-tooltip" title="Edit on GitHub"><span class="fa fa-pencil"></span></a>
                                                                    <p>In the test, the <code>Programmer</code> is <em>owned</em> by <code>weaverryan</code> and then we authenticate
as <code>weaverryan</code>. So, we're starting a battle using a Programmer that <em>we</em> own. Time
to mess that up. Create a new user called <code>someone_else</code>:</p>
