<p>Run the test to see the failure:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">./vendor/bin/phpunit --filter testPOSTBattleValidationErrors</div></code></pre>
<p>Yep: there's no error for <code>programmerId</code> yet.</p>
<p>Let's fix that. Right now, the client can pass <em>any</em> valid programmer id, and the
<code>EntityType</code> happily accepts it. To shrink that to a smaller list, we'll pass it
a custom query to use.</p>
<h2 id="passing-the-user-to-the-form">Passing the User to the Form <a class="headerlink" href="restrict-valid-programmer-input#passing-the-user-to-the-form" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
