<h2 id="passing-the-query-builder-option">Passing the query_builder Option <a class="headerlink" href="restrict-valid-programmer-input#passing-the-query-builder-option" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
