        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>
</p>
<p>Inside, <code>return $this-&gt;createQueryBuilder()</code> and alias the class to <code>programmer</code>.
Then, just <code>andWhere('programmer.user = :user')</code> with <code>-&gt;setParameter('user', $user)</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="1141d82b1d">
