<p>Run it!</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">./vendor/bin/phpunit --filter testPOSTBattleValidationErrors</div></code></pre>
<p>So that's "sanity" validation: it's form fields watching your back to make sure
mean users don't start sending crazy things to us. And it happens automatically.</p>

    
